===Verb===
{{en-verb|quibble|quibbles|quibbled|quibbling}}
#''(intransitive)'' To [[complain]] or [[argue]] in a [[trivial]] or [[petty]] manner.
#:''They are contsantly '''quibbling''' over insignifiant details.''
